            <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>CAN SPAM&nbsp; Act :</strong></span></p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000;">The CAN-SPAM Act is a law that sets the rules for commercial email, establishes requirements for commercial messages, gives </span><span style="color: #000000;">recipients the right to have emails stopped from being sent to them, and spells out tough penalties for violations.</span><span style="color: #000000;">We collect your email address in order to:</span><span style="color: #000000;">Send information, respond to inquiries, and/or other requests or questions To be in accordance with CANSPAM, we agree to the </span><span style="color: #000000;">following:</span>
